steps.name: Create the Folder: First_Folder
Click 'New Item' on sidebar menu
Type First_Folder to name input field
Select 'Folder' and click 'Ok' button
Click on the button 'Save'
Click on the Jenkins logo on the header
Create the Folder: Folder_to_move_into_the_first
Click 'New Item' on sidebar menu
Type Folder_to_move_into_the_first to name input field
Select 'Folder' and click 'Ok' button
Click on the button 'Save'
Click on the Jenkins logo on the header
Click 'Folder_to_move_into_the_first' Folder name
Hover cursor over project name on breadcrumbs to show arrow
Click breadcrumbs arrow after project name to call menu
Click 'Move' on the breadcrumbs dropdown Menu
Select the destination Folder to move the project
Click 'Move' button when moved via breadcrumbs
Click breadcrumbs arrow after project name to call menu
Get first item name inside Folder
